ok so this sounds so stupid but what does p s mean again it means post script and is used to add something at the end of a letter or message that you forgot to add to the actual body of the letter or message example dear aunt sally i thank you so much for the hospitality you gave me yesterday at your house i enjoyed the tea and buiscits please try to keep in touch with me as much as possible love saadia p s i absolutely love the decorations in your house so exotic Fibber McGee and Molly Cloud Lightning Severe weather terminology (United States) Cumulonimbus cloud Old-time radio Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children Johnny Carson The Price Is Right Star Wars Episode V: The Empire Strikes Back Catch phrase The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Tertiary to Quintessential Phases Highlander: The Series Galveston Hurricane of 1900 Supercell Bill Thompson (voice actor) The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson Superman III Soap opera As the World Turns Political correctness The Flintstones Tornado Columbine High School massacre The Six Million Dollar Man Rowan & Martin's Laugh-In Krakatoa Funnel cloud Captain Marvel (DC Comics) William S. Burroughs 1980 eruption of Mount St. Helens Search for Tomorrow Academy Award for Original Music Score Pok__mon The Parting of the Ways Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace National Weather Service Mercury Atlas 6 Thunderstorm World Series The Wizard of Oz (1939 film) Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Monsoon Professional wrestling double-team maneuvers Sex Pistols Serial Whose Line Is It Anyway? Weather lore Air traffic control HarperCollins The Amber Spyglass 2004 World Series Suspense St. Cloud, Minnesota Open cluster Climate of the United Kingdom Doctor Who (Enemy Within) Pilot Reports TV-FM DX Pittsburgh Steelers The Amazing Race Fox News Weekend Update (sketch) Philosophy of language Phrase Euphemism K__ppen climate classification The Adventures of Pete & Pete Hiberno-English The Doctor Dances Dog agility Oort cloud Thunderbirds